==English==

===Noun===

'''meiofauna''' (''plural'' '''meiofaunae''' or '''meiofaunas''')

# A type of [[interstitial fauna]], such as [[psammon]], found in [[rock]] [[fissure]]s, between the [[grain]]s of loose [[sediment]]s, on [[algae]], etc. It is a part of the [[microfauna]].

